title: Aleksandr Ivankov
text:
Aleksandr Alekseyevich Ivankov (; born 12 January 2000) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Metallurg%20Lipetsk">FC Metallurg Lipetsk</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Metallurg%20Lipetsk">FC Metallurg Lipetsk</a> on 25 July 2021 in a game against <a href="FC%20Akron%20Tolyatti">FC Akron Tolyatti</a>.
